%28HD%29.webm/Pointing_and_Calling_Japanese_Safety_Standard_at_Railway_Companies_%26_Toyota_%28HD%29.webm.160p.webm&quot; type=&quot;video/webm; codecs=&amp;quot;vp8, vorbis&amp;quot;&quot; data-title=&quot;Low bandwidth WebM (160P)&quot; data-shorttitle=&quot;WebM 160P&quot; data-transcodekey=&quot;160p.webm&quot; data-width=&quot;284&quot; data-height=&quot;160&quot; data-bandwidth=&quot;216344&quot; data-framerate=&quot;29.97&quot;/&gt;&lt;source src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/transcoded/8/8b/Pointing_and_Calling_Japanese_Safety_Standard_at_Railway_Companies_%26_Toyota_%28HD%29.webm/Pointing_and_Calling_Japanese_Safety_Standard_at_Railway_Companies_%26_Toyota_%28HD%29.webm.240p.webm&quot; type=&quot;video/webm; codecs=&amp;quot;vp8, vorbis&amp;quot;&quot; data-title=&quot;Small WebM (240P)&quot; data-shorttitle=&quot;WebM 240P&quot; data-transcodekey=&quot;240p.webm&quot; data-width=&quot;426&quot; data-height=&quot;240&quot; data-bandwidth=&quot;322248&quot; data-framerate=&quot;29.97&quot;/&gt;&lt;source src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/transcoded/8/8b/Pointing_and_Calling_Japanese_Safety_Standard_at_Railway_Companies_%26_Toyota_%28HD%29.webm/Pointing_and_Calling_Japanese_Safety_Standard_at_Railway_Companies_%26_Toyota_%28HD%29.webm.360p.webm&quot; type=&quot;video/webm; codecs=&amp;quot;vp8, vorbis&amp;quot;&quot; data-title=&quot;WebM (360P)&quot; data-shorttitle=&quot;WebM 360P&quot; data-transcodekey=&quot;360p.webm&quot; data-width=&quot;640&quot; data-height=&quot;360&quot; data-bandwidth=&quot;576464&quot; data-framerate=&quot;29.97&quot;/&gt;&lt;/video&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\"><img alt=\"File:Pointing and Calling Japanese Safety Standard at Railway Companies &amp; Toyota (HD).webm\" style=\"width:220px;height:124px\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8b/Pointing_and_Calling_Japanese_Safety_Standard_at_Railway_Companies_%26_Toyota_%28HD%29.webm/220px--Pointing_and_Calling_Japanese_Safety_Standard_at_Railway_Companies_%26_Toyota_%28HD%29.webm.jpg\" /><a href=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8b/Pointing_and_Calling_Japanese_Safety_Standard_at_Railway_Companies_%26_Toyota_%28HD%29.webm\" title=\"Play media\" target=\"new\"><span class=\"play-btn-large\"><span class=\"mw-tmh-playtext\">Play media</span></span></a></div>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Pointing_and_Calling_Japanese_Safety_Standard_at_Railway_Companies_%26_Toyota_(HD).webm\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>(video) different train operators and factory workers using Pointing and Calling.</div></div></div>\n<p>Pointing and calling requires co-action and co-reaction among the operator's <a href=\"/wiki/Human_brain\" title=\"Human brain\">brain</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Human_eye\" title=\"Human eye\">eyes</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Hands\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hands\">hands</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Mouth\" title=\"Mouth\">mouth</a>, and <a href=\"/wiki/Ears\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ears\">ears</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Effectiveness\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Effectiveness</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Further_reading\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Further reading</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Pointing_and_calling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The method originated in Japan in the early 1900s, with train drivers calling out the status of signals. The pointing was added a few decades later.<sup id=\"cite_ref-japantimes_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-japantimes-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Effectiveness\">Effectiveness</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Pointing_and_calling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Effectiveness\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>A 1994 study by the <a href=\"/wiki/Railway_Technical_Research_Institute\" title=\"Railway Technical Research Institute\">Railway Technical Research Institute</a> showed that pointing and calling reduced mistakes by almost 85 percent when doing a simple task.<sup id=\"cite_ref-japantimes_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-japantimes-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Pointing_and_calling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-japantimes-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-japantimes_1-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-japantimes_1-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-japantimes_1-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Gordenker, Alice (October 21, 2008). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2008/10/21/reference/jr-gestures/#.VL7Xg-d2MTk\">\"JR gestures\"</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/The_Japan_Times\" title=\"The Japan Times\">The Japan Times</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2008-12-05</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=JR+gestures&amp;rft.pub=The+Japan+Times&amp;rft.date=2008-10-21&amp;rft.aulast=Gordenker&amp;rft.aufirst=Alice&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.japantimes.co.jp%2Fnews%2F2008%2F10%2F21%2Freference%2Fjr-gestures%2F%23.VL7Xg-d2MTk&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APointing+and+calling\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.is/20110716123642/http://www.jica.go.jp/english/operations/evaluation/jica_archive/project/term/latin_america/mexico_2001_3.html\">\"Terminal Evaluation - Latin America and the Caribbean\"</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Japan_International_Cooperation_Agency\" title=\"Japan International Cooperation Agency\">Japan International Cooperation Agency</a>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.jica.go.jp/english/operations/evaluation/jica_archive/project/term/latin_america/mexico_2001_3.html\">the original</a> on 2011-07-16<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2008-12-05</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Terminal+Evaluation+-+Latin+America+and+the+Caribbean&amp;rft.pub=Japan+International+Cooperation+Agency&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jica.go.jp%2Fenglish%2Foperations%2Fevaluation%2Fjica_archive%2Fproject%2Fterm%2Flatin_america%2Fmexico_2001_3.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APointing+and+calling\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Further_reading\">Further reading</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Pointing_and_calling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Further reading\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>\u7530\u8fba\u8087 \"\u5371\u967a\u4e88\u77e5\u6d3b\u52d5\u5b9f\u8df5\u30de\u30cb\u30e5\u30a2\u30eb\" 1984, <a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Japan_Industrial_Safety_and_Health_Association&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Japan Industrial Safety and Health Association (page does not exist)\">Japan Industrial Safety and Health Association</a></li>\n<li>\u4eca\u6751\u4e00\u90ce \"\u6a5f\u95a2\u8eca\u3068\u5171\u306b\" 1962\u3001\u30d8\u30c3\u30c9\u30e9\u30a4\u30c8\u793e, page 78</li>\n<li>\u795e\u6238\u9244\u9053\u7ba1\u7406\u5c40 \"\u6a5f\u95a2\u8eca\u4e57\u52d9\u54e1\u6559\u7bc4\" 1913\u5e74, pages 259-262</li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation news\">Kazumitsu Shinoharaa, Hiroshi Naitoa (Graduate School of Human Sciences, Osaka University) Yuko Matsuib, Masaru Hikonob (Institute of Nuclear Safety System, Japan) (March 2013). \"The effects of \"finger pointing and calling\" on cognitive control processes in the task-switching paradigm\". <i>International Journal of Industrial Ergonomics</i>. <b>43</b> (2). pp.&#160;129\u2013136. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1016/j.ergon.2012.08.004\">10.1016/j.ergon.2012.08.004</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=International+Journal+of+Industrial+Ergonomics&amp;rft.atitle=The+effects+of+%E2%80%9Cfinger+pointing+and+calling%E2%80%9D+on+cognitive+control+processes+in+the+task-switching+paradigm&amp;rft.volume=43&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=129-136&amp;rft.date=2013-03&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1016%2Fj.ergon.2012.08.004&amp;rft.au=Kazumitsu+Shinoharaa%2C+Hiroshi+Naitoa+%28Graduate+School+of+Human+Sciences%2C+Osaka+University%29+Yuko+Matsuib%2C+Masaru+Hikonob+%28Institute+of+Nuclear+Safety+System%2C+Japan%29&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APointing+and+calling\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span><span class=\"citation-comment\" style=\"display:none; color:#33aa33; margin-left:0.3em\">CS1 maint: Multiple names: authors list (<a href=\"/wiki/Category:CS1_maint:_Multiple_names:_authors_list\" title=\"Category:CS1 maint: Multiple names: authors list\">link</a>) </span></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Pointing_and_calling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table role=\"presentation\" class=\"mbox-small plainlinks sistersitebox\" style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9;border:1px solid #aaa;color:#000\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"mbox-image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4a/Commons-logo.svg/30px-Commons-logo.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"40\" class=\"noviewer\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4a/Commons-logo.svg/45px